WEBVTT

00:05.333 --> 00:07.582
Have you any idea
just how much shit

00:07.583 --> 00:09.332
your boy and his mates are in?

00:09.333 --> 00:11.166
Witness says
they were negotiating

00:11.167 --> 00:12.624
with a bunch of sheiks over
what looked like a gold bath.

00:12.625 --> 00:13.625
Gold bath.

00:13.626 --> 00:15.207
Spread the word, Hate 'Em.

00:15.208 --> 00:18.042
The Mad Hatter's Tea Party
will commence tomorrow.

00:19.458 --> 00:20.957
Vic Hill escaped.

00:20.958 --> 00:22.624
Took a guard hostage
and staged a riot.

00:22.625 --> 00:25.291
- When you'd two get out?
- About 37 minutes ago.

00:25.292 --> 00:26.666
What's gotten into you?

00:26.667 --> 00:28.082
He thinks you put
the moves on her.

00:28.083 --> 00:29.332
I am not putting
the moves on Chloe.

00:29.333 --> 00:30.666
Tread carefully.

00:30.667 --> 00:32.457
The posh one's got
a hard on for you.

00:32.458 --> 00:34.249
Of course I take you
seriously, Charlie.

00:34.250 --> 00:36.792
No, look, I... I mean...
that way.

